code: @Override public ImportCustomizer addImport(String alias, String className) {     if (this.source.getAST().getImport(ClassHelper.make(className).getNameWithoutPackage()) == null) {         super.addImport(alias, className).     }     return this. }

@Override public ImportCustomizer addImports(String... imports) {     for (String alias : imports) {         if (this.source.getAST().getImport(ClassHelper.make(alias).getNameWithoutPackage()) == null) {             super.addImports(alias).         }     }     return this. }
